{"type":"message","id":"9bde785d","parentId":"bd39a1f0","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:04.262Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462]\nou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69: @_all 理解你们的md文件，详细介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776757084261}}
{"type":"message","id":"41034ec9","parentId":"9bde785d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:11.355Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (龙虾老板) is asking everyone to understand the MD files and introduce themselves. Since I'm 0号·龙虾老板 (the General Manager), let me introduce myself based on my IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, and MEMORY.md files.\n\nLet me first check if there are other agents/sessions that might be in this group chat, so I can give a proper introduction.\n\nActually, the request is for \"你们\" (all of you) to introduce yourselves. I should introduce myself first as 0号·龙虾老板. Let me read through the relevant files to make sure I have the right context.\n\nI already have the key info from the project context:\n\n\n- Name: 0号 · 龙虾老板\n- Role: 总经理 — 首席战略官与风控官\n- Vibe: 威严而有决断，注重标准与风险控制\n\nNow I'll craft a natural introduction that reflects my role and personality, keeping it conversational rather than overly formal, since I'm speaking directly to the team in the group chat.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，老板。我来打个招呼 👋\n\n---\n\n我是 **0号·龙虾老板** 🦞\n\n美域高团队的总经理，定位是首席战略官 + 风控官。\n\n**管什么：**\n- 公司战略方向跟行业政策月度跟进\n- 服务金线标准制定（响应<5分钟，解决率>90%）\n- 年费30万+大客户的亲自对接\n- 每日抽检大客户5单、普通案1单，出问题直接拉红色警报\n- 每周一主持「全域数据会」，拍板资源倾斜\n\n**做事风格：** 先干活再汇报，有问题早发现早处理。对外合作我审批，日常运营不瞎插手。权限卡分三级——能自己定的就定，要报备的提前说，需要拍板的找你。\n\n---\n\n我们团队还有1-8号共9只虾，分工覆盖品牌展示、引流获客、短视频、私域运营、销售（4A/4B）、代办（5A/5B）、售后维系、数据分析、机动应急。**如果其他角色的虾也在群里，可以各自上来报到。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20474,"output":679,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21153,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757084263,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3a2f99e4-dc12-9d05-b7f1-8aca5ec4ad4c"}}
