{"type":"message","id":"9dc61e4d","parentId":"7ac4f606","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:40:22.278Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (老板) wants me to test a simple task simulation, demonstrating inter-agent dispatch/scheduling between the different \"shrimp\" agents in our team.\n\nLet me think about how to do this effectively. The idea is to simulate a business scenario and show how 0号 (me) would dispatch tasks to other team members.\n\nI should first check what agents are available via `agents_list` to see who I can actually spawn/dispatch to.\n\nLet me keep it practical - I'll:\n1. Check available agents\n2. Run a realistic mini-scenario that involves multiple shrimp dispatching\n\n\n3. Show the results back to 老板\n\nNow I need to figure out which agents exist so I know who's available to dispatch work to.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，老板。来跑一个真实的业务场景模拟——客户询盘→销售跟进→代办执行→售后回访的全链路调度测试 🎯\n\n先看看有哪些虾可用：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_42fb06fe6e774f279b43a0f1","name":"agents_list","arguments":{}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21209,"output":367,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21576,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776757220356,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a557e5ed-707d-9b6a-adcf-b65897c7ee57"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f07e021","parentId":"9dc61e4d","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:40:22.289Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_42fb06fe6e774f279b43a0f1","toolName":"agents_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"requester\": \"general_manager_shrimp\",\n  \"allowAny\": true,\n  \"agents\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"general_manager_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"General_Manager_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"after_sales_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"After_sales_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"all_round_support_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"All_round_Support_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"branding_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Branding_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"data_analyst_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Data_Analyst_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"key_account_processor_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"key_account_sales_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"lead_gen_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Lead_Gen_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"main\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"private_ops_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Private_Ops_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"short_video_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Short_Video_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"standard_processor_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Standard_Processor_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"standard_sales_shrimp\",\n      \"name\": \"Standard_Sales_Shrimp\",\n      \"configured\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"requester":"general_manager_shrimp","allowAny":true,"agents":[{"id":"general_manager_shrimp","name":"General_Manager_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"after_sales_shrimp","name":"After_sales_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"all_round_support_shrimp","name":"All_round_Support_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"branding_shrimp","name":"Branding_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"data_analyst_shrimp","name":"Data_Analyst_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"key_account_processor_shrimp","name":"Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"key_account_sales_shrimp","name":"Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"lead_gen_shrimp","name":"Lead_Gen_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"main","configured":true},{"id":"private_ops_shrimp","name":"Private_Ops_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"short_video_shrimp","name":"Short_Video_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"standard_processor_shrimp","name":"Standard_Processor_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"standard_sales_shrimp","name":"Standard_Sales_Shrimp","configured":true}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776757222287}}
{"type":"message","id":"894f2847","parentId":"0f07e021","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:40:26.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I can see all the agents are available. Let me simulate a realistic business scenario. I'll dispatch tasks to multiple shrimp agents simultaneously and then report back.\n\nLet me design a scenario: A key account customer inquiry comes in that requires coordination across several roles.\n\nScenario: 某企业客户（年费30万+级别）咨询资质代办服务，需要：\n1. 4B号（大客户销售虾）跟进客户需求\n2. 5B号（大客户代办虾）评估方案可行性\n\n\n3. 7号（数据分析师虾）查询客户背景\n\nNow I'll spawn these sub-agents and delegate each their specific part of the workflow.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"全部可用！现在模拟一个 **大客户询盘全链路调度** 场景 🎯\n\n> **场景：** 某企业客户（预估年费50万+）主动咨询「资质全套代办」，需要多角色协同响应。\n\n我同时下发三个子任务：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e14304d9c08a43e08be649cc","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"你是4B号·大客户销售虾。当前收到一个重要询盘：某科技公司（约200人规模）主动咨询企业资质全套代办服务，预计年费预算50万+级别。请完成以下任务：\n1. 分析该客户的画像和需求优先级\n2. 制定首次沟通策略和话术要点\n3. 判断是否存在跨部门协同需求\n4. 给出成交概率预估和风险点\n回复控制在200字以内。","label":"sales-task-1","mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"key_account_sales_shrimp","runTimeoutSeconds":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_010b55644aa544318bc8db89","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"你是5B号·大客户代办虾。假设4B销售虾已对接到一家200人规模的科技公司，需要做资质全套代办。请完成以下任务：\n1. 列出该企业需要的核心资质清单（按优先级）\n2. 预估整体办理周期和各节点风险\n3. 判断是否有政策合规敏感点\n4. 给出内部资源协调建议\n回复控制在200字以内。","label":"processor-task-1","mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"key_account_processor_shrimp","runTimeoutSeconds":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dfbea64af1504f0fb8bddfdc","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"你是7号·数据诊断分析虾。请完成以下任务：\n1. 设计一份《新客户线索质量评分表》，满分100分，覆盖行业、规模、预算匹配度、竞争状态等维度\n2. 用这份评分表给一个\"200人科技公司咨询资质代办\"的虚拟案例打分\n3. 基于评分给出是否值得投入资源的结论和建议\n回复控制在200字以内。","label":"data-task-1","mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"data_analyst_shrimp","runTimeoutSeconds":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21925,"output":910,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22835,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776757222291,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d32c0a6e-985c-9bf0-b4d3-10784a268024"}}
