{"type":"message","id":"8a3904c0","parentId":"d26d310f","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:40:29.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've spawned 3 sub-agents. Let me wait for their completions and then compile a summary report for the boss.\n\nThe three sessions are:\n1. key_account_sales_shrimp - sales analysis\n2. key_account_processor_shrimp - processor feasibility\n3. data_analyst_shrimp - scoring evaluation\n\nI'll wait for all three to complete.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已同时下发三个任务，等待各虾汇报... 📋\n\n- **4B号·大客户销售虾** → 客户画像与成交策略\n- **5B号·大客户代办虾** → 资质清单与合规评估\n- **7号·数据诊断分析虾** → 线索质量评分\n\n等结果汇总后给您一份完整调度报告。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":23310,"output":238,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23548,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757226842,"responseId":"chatcmpl-98e1fb56-bf67-9b8f-afb1-fa83ed169972"}}
