{"type":"message","id":"fd58cbc3","parentId":"f04288a6","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:42:04.480Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146ea6fe8b8c38ce1a945d2b6b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:42 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146ea6fe8b8c38ce1a945d2b6b]\nou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69: 为什么子代理不会再调用其他子代理，这是个公司团队，所有人都要参与进来，你再试试模拟一个任务。\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_ccee94c267e8f9d0b4e40d93a0f54a77\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1776757324479}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0332f8b","parentId":"fd58cbc3","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:42:10.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板说得对——刚才的模拟是\"0号→3个虾\"的单层分发，但实际上公司是一个完整团队，各虾之间应该能互相调度。子代理应该有能力继续调用其他子代理来完成任务。\n\n让我重新理解：子代理（subagent）在执行任务时，如果它需要其他角色协作，它自己也应该能够 spawn 新的 subagent。这就像一个销售虾在接到询盘后，发现自己需要数据支持，可以主动叫数据分析虾来帮忙。\n\n刚才的问题可能是：\n1. 我下发的任务可能没有包含\"你需要与其他虾协同\"的条件\n\n\n2. 子代理确实有 spawn 能力，但任务指令里没有引导它们去用这个能力\n\n现在我要设计一个更复杂的场景——一个大客户询盘，需要多角色层层转发和协作，这样每个虾在被调用时都能继续调度下一环。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板说得对，我上次的模拟太浅了——只有0号直接派活，缺少真正的\"跨虾协作\"链路。公司团队不应该是树状派发，而应该是有机的协作网络。\n\n这次我来跑一个**多轮接力式**调度：先给第一只虾派活，然后它在执行过程中自己发现需要其他角色支援，从而**主动召唤下一波虾**。\n\n场景：**突发危机事件**——某大客户投诉要公开曝光 🚨\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aefe4e372cf94714b2a5bfb2","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"你是6号·售后维系虾。你现在收到一封紧急邮件：一位年费45万的大客户负责人私下联系你，表示他们的资质代办已经延误了15天（原定昨天办结），情绪非常激动，威胁要在社交媒体公开发文曝光我们\"收钱不办事\"。\n\n请完成以下任务：\n1. 评估该事件的舆情风险和等级\n2. 起草一份给客户的情绪安抚话术（控制在100字内）\n3. **关键决策：** 根据问题原因，你需要向哪些同事发出协请求？明确告诉他们你要\"调用\"他们做什么事。（这是真实的公司内部调度，不是比喻！用 exec/sessions_spawn 等实际工具去拉人过来。）","label":"urgent-crisis-6","mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"after_sales_shrimp","runTimeoutSeconds":90}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":26413,"output":705,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27118,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776757324481,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4c534c74-bd8b-9461-b6a9-edb30b56e9e7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5b1c66b","parentId":"a0332f8b","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:42:11.130Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_aefe4e372cf94714b2a5bfb2","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:after_sales_shrimp:subagent:8362473f-0051-4916-b8a6-d7ffd0b4be5d\",\n  \"runId\": \"3b2f153f-b238-4e40-8203-21ac54bc807c\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}"}],"details":{"status":"accepted","childSessionKey":"agent:after_sales_shrimp:subagent:8362473f-0051-4916-b8a6-d7ffd0b4be5d","runId":"3b2f153f-b238-4e40-8203-21ac54bc807c","mode":"run","note":"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.","modelApplied":true},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776757331129}}
{"type":"message","id":"3091ce8d","parentId":"d5b1c66b","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:42:12.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I've spawned the first subagent (after_sales_shrimp/6号). The task explicitly instructs it to use sessions_spawn/exec tools to call other team members if needed. Let me wait for its completion before deciding next steps.\n\nThe note says \"do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool\" - so I just wait for the push notification.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，已派发第一棒给 **6号·售后维系虾** ——任务是处理危机事件并**自主发起跨岗位协请求**。等它处理完发现需要支援后，会主动召唤其他虾加入。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":27152,"output":212,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757331130,"responseId":"chatcmpl-75c45d60-5a36-9bf4-bdde-a12199c2863e"}}
