{"type":"message","id":"c3731632","parentId":"954127cb","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:42:42.403Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've spawned 5 sub-agents for the crisis response. Now I need to wait for all of them to complete before presenting the full results. Let me summarize what's been sent out and wait for the completion events.\n\nThe agents I spawned:\n1. **5B·大客户代办虾** — 根因分析 + 补救方案\n2. **4B·大客户销售虾** — 外部应对 + 客户话术\n3. **1号·品牌展示虾** — 公关预案\n4. **7号·数据诊断分析虾** — 数据支持\n\n\n5. **8号·机动应急打杂虾** — 后勤协调\n\nThat gives me a solid cross-functional team ready to handle this from multiple angles. I'll hold off on sending anything until all five agents finish their tasks, then present the consolidated findings.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，老板。第一棒6号上报危机后，我作为0号立刻拉起**全员应急响应机制**，5路并行派发：\n\n| 虾 | 任务 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 🔴 **5B·代办虾** | 延误根因分析 + 补救方案 | ⏳ 执行中 |\n| 🟠 **4B·销售虾** | 客户紧急话术 + 谈判策略 | ⏳ 执行中 |\n| 🟡 **1号·品牌虾** | 舆情预警等级 + 公关预案 | ⏳ 执行中 |\n| 🟢 **7号·数据虾** | 延误率统计框架 + 数据弹药 | ⏳ 执行中 |\n| 🔵 **8号·打杂虾** | 24小时应急待办清单 + P0事务顶上去 | ⏳ 执行中 |\n\n等全部到齐，我会给您一份完整的红色警报处置报告，包含各岗位的协作关系网。正在收集中... 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":29947,"output":589,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30536,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757358331,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8138db1d-2d11-9e27-8783-e63a0ca6e347"}}
