{"type":"message","id":"044adffd","parentId":"03cdc7e5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:45:45.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if all 11 other shrimp participated. Let me count:\n\nFrom the first simulation (customer inquiry):\n- 4B sales ✅\n- 5B processor ✅\n- 7 data ✅\n\nFrom the second simulation (crisis):\n- 6 after-sales ✅\n- 5B processor ✅ (already counted)\n- 4B sales ✅ (already counted)\n- 1 branding ✅\n- 7 data ✅ (already counted)\n- 8 support ✅\n\nTotal unique participants: 4B, 5B, 7, 6, 1, 8 = 6 shrimp\n\n\nThat leaves out 2 lead gen, 3 short video, 3+ private ops, 4A standard sales, and 5A standard processor. I'm now running a Q2 planning task to involve all remaining team members.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"坦白说：**没有。** 上次两个模拟加起来只派了6只虾，还有6只是闲置的。是我的问题——场景选得太窄了。\n\n刚才我补了一个 **\"Q2季度冲刺全员作战规划\"** 的场景，把剩下的 **5只** 也拉上了：\n\n| # | 虾 | 状态 | 任务 |\n|---|-----|------|------|\n| 1 | 2号·引流获客 | ⏳ 派发中 | 渠道效率分析 + Q2线索量计算 |\n| 2 | 3号·短视频 | ⏳ 派发中 | 各平台内容策略 + 发布计划 |\n| 3 | 3+号·私域运营 | ⏳ 派发中 | 3000客户分层激活 + 营销日历 |\n| 4 | 4A·普通销售 | ⏳ 派发中 | 20条待跟进线索评估 + 业绩拆解 |\n| 5 | 5A·普通代办 | ⏳ 派发中 | 50个在手订单盘点 + SOP优化建议 |\n\n加上之前参与过的 **1品牌、4B销售、5B代办、6售后、7数据、8打杂**，这次目标就是让**全部12只虾（含我自己）同时在线工作**。\n\n等结果陆续回来我会给您一个完整的\"全员到齐报告\" 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":38263,"output":674,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38937,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757534643,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5543a307-a86a-9cc7-99e0-58012780ae9d"}}
