{"type":"message","id":"327fedf9","parentId":"c8a21134","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:52:29.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to simulate a Food Production License (食品生产许可证/SC证) task. I've already spawned 6 agents in parallel:\n- 4B·大客户销售虾 - client assessment & quoting\n- 5A·普通资质代办虾 - processing plan & checklist\n- 7号·数据分析虾 - market data & pricing reference\n- 6号·售后维系虾 - post-license maintenance\n- 2号·引流获客虾 - lead generation strategy\n- 1号·品牌展示虾 - brand positioning\n \nNow I'll wait for the results to come back from each agent, then compile them together into a complete overview.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，老板！**食品生产许可证(SC证)** 全流程模拟已启动 🍱🔖\n\n6路并行派发——\n\n| 虾 | 任务方向 | 状态 |\n|---|---------|------|\n| 4B·大客户销售 | 客户画像 + 报价策略 + 弹药清单 | ⏳ |\n| 5A·普通代办 | 材料清单 + 办理流程 + 现场核查准备 + 驳回TOP5 | ⏳ |\n| 7号·数据分析 | 市场对标 + 价格区间 + 风险信号 + 竞品分析弹药 | ⏳ |\n| 6号·售后维系 | 年审续证提醒 + 延伸销售机会 + 投诉预防 | ⏳ |\n| 2号·引流获客 | 精准渠道 + 内容素材 + 诱饵设计 | ⏳ |\n| 1号·品牌展示 | 专业感包装 + 案例呈现 + 差异化卖点提炼 | ⏳ |\n\n这是从前端获客→中端销售→后端代办→售后维护的**完整业务链路**。等结果回来给您一份完整的方案报告 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":46703,"output":523,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47226,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757944829,"responseId":"chatcmpl-19e65b19-4e9a-9809-981f-5d4545b174d2"}}
