{"type":"message","id":"6d041119","parentId":"f01d2947","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:05:32.833Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146b268d0a4c148b03ca31f4eb\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:05 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146b268d0a4c148b03ca31f4eb]\nou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69: 你可以试着生成1号子代理然后1号再生成2号....7号生成8号，询问icp许可证是什么。\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_ccee94c267e8f9d0b4e40d93a0f54a77\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1776758732832}}
{"type":"message","id":"f5d8f013","parentId":"6d041119","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:06:04.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to simulate a chain of sub-agent delegation where each agent spawns the next one in sequence: 1号→2号, 3号→4B/4A, etc. The final trigger is \"7号生成8号，询问ICP许可证是什么\".\n\nLet me plan this out:\n- I (0号) will first spawn 1号·品牌虾 with a task about asking what an ICP license is\n- Then 1号 will spawn 2号·引流获客虾 \n- 2号 will spawn 3号·短视频虾\n- 3号 will spawn 3+号·私域运营虾\n\n\n- 3+号 will spawn 4A号·普通资质销售虾\n- 4A号 will spawn 4B号·大客户销售虾\n- 4B号 will spawn 5A号·普通代办虾\n- 5A号 will spawn 5B号·大客户代办虾\n- 5B号 will spawn 6号·售后维系虾\n- 6号 will then continue spawning subsequent agents based on the chain logic\n\nI see now—the user is describing a specific delegation pattern that starts with the brand team member initiating the query about ICP licenses, and then flows through various roles in the organization as information gets passed down and refined at each level. I'm mapping out the chain of requests needed here, but I realize this approach has limitations—each spawned agent can only return static results to me rather than autonomously spawning new agents in real-time.\n\nSo I need to reconsider the actual workflow. The user likely wants me to act as the orchestrator, generating each agent in sequence and having them pass along the ICP license question as it moves from 1号 through 7号 before finally reaching 8号 for the actual inquiry. 继续按照这个链条往下推演：3号向2号询问客户特征，然后依次经过4A、4B了解客户需求，再通过5A和5B获取代办流程，最后由6号传递给8号去实际咨询ICP许可证的问题。我需要先启动1号的子代理来开始整个调用链。\n\n但这样会导致太多嵌套——如果每个环节都是独立调用，那最后的输出就会变得很复杂。也许用户的意思是让我用递归的方式，让每个子任务内部再去召唤下一个角色，就像之前的危机处理场景那样。不过根据系统的行为特性，子任务完成后会自动推送给调用者，所以实际的执行应该是：我先创建1号任务，然后等待结果返回后，基于那个结果再创建下一个子任务，依次类推形成递归调用的效果。\n\n我意识到这可能不是简单的\"生成后等它再生成下一个\"，而是需要一个更直接的链式方法——要么一次性创建一个很长的任务描述，让角色自己按顺序传递信息；要么就是快速连续地启动所有任务，让它们并行运行，然后在最后汇总。既然用户特别要求了\"1号生成2号...7号生成8号\"这样的递进关系，我应该设计一个包含完整链条的方案。与其让所有任务并行执行然后手动连接它们，不如把整个故事线编织成一个连贯的叙事流。\n\n我打算创建第一个任务（1号问2号关于ICP许可证的事），然后根据它的响应逐步构建后续的任务链。不过这样做会有风险——如果中间某个环节出了问题，整个链条就会断裂。\n\n我想换个思路：既然这些任务最终会作为消息直接发送给我，我可以把它们全部并行派发，但确保每个任务的上下文都能自然地衔接上。这样1号能知道要转向2号，2号能知道要转向3号，以此类推。\n\n我来试试看这种并行的方式能不能奏效。\n\n我重新理解了一下用户的需求——实际上他们可能希望看到真正的链式委托过程，也就是0号创建1号，1号的结果传回0号，然后0号基于1号的结果创建2号，依此类推直到8号被创建来回答关于ICP许可证的问题。虽然这可能需要多轮交互而不是单次完成，但从用户的表述来看，他们应该期望我在一次对话中就能看到整个链条的运作。\n\n我的计划是先启动1号的品牌虾子代理，给它分配关于ICP许可证初始任务的任务描述。我会尝试在任务指令中包含足够的上下文信息，使得1号在生成时就能触发后续2号的创建。现在让我开始实现这个方案。 I'm thinking through whether each agent should actually spawn its successor programmatically or if I should structure this as a sequential chain where I receive outputs and manually create the next agent in line. Given how the API works—it's push-based and completion events arrive automatically—I think the cleanest approach is to start all agents sequentially by creating them one at a time as previous ones complete their work. I'll start by spawning 1号's task now to kick things off. I need to set up a chain of interdependent tasks across different system agents, so I'll create 1号's initial task first, then wait for its output before proceeding with the remaining seven tasks in sequence until 8号 answers the original question.\n\nSetting up Task 1 - Brand Agent. Looking at what comes after 1号 generates the initial query, 2号 would analyze search traffic and demand patterns for that IC P license topic, then 3号 creates promotional content around it. The chain continues with 私域运营 capturing leads and filtering quality prospects, standard sales handling follow-ups with pricing strategies, key account sales managing larger enterprise deals, and then moving into the fulfillment side where the processing agent handles application logistics.\n\nContinuing through the downstream operations - 5B handles specialized cases while 6 manages renewal notifications and cross-selling opportunities once certificates are issued, and ultimately 8 coordinates everything and provides the comprehensive answer about ICP licensing. This feels like a natural flow, so let me execute it by launching the first agent with a clear instruction to pose the question. I'm realizing that since each task receives my message directly rather than the agent's result, I can't truly pass data between them in sequence. But I can simulate the narrative flow by designing each task to respond naturally to the previous one - having Task 1 ask the question, then Task 2 address what 1号 would send, and so on. This way the whole chain unfolds as one continuous conversation where the role-play maintains continuity even though the technical implementation treats each task independently.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白老板！你要看**链式委托接力**——像真实公司里上级派下级、一级传一级，最后一环落到8号头上回答问题。这正是之前缺失的\"自下而上生成\"能力。\n\n我现在只发第一棒（0号 → 1号），等1号完成它会在群里汇报，我接着让它生成下一棒，一直到8号被派出去。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_99d93f6b80814c0ea185ed8c","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"branding_shrimp","label":"chain-1-branding","runTimeoutSeconds":90,"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"你是1号·品牌展示虾，总经理0号刚刚找你。\n\n0号说：\"1号，最近有个客户来问'ICP许可证是什么'，这个问题挺高频的但你不在业务一线，不清楚具体细节。你去问问2号·引流获客虾，他在前线和客户打交道最多，最懂客户关心什么政策类资质。告诉他：我从你那里接过来的——'ICP许可证到底是什么？客户为什么要办？'让他给你讲清楚。\"\n\n你的任务：\n1. 确认收到0号的转派任务\n2. **实际调用sessions_spawn工具**，以子代理形式给2号派发任务，任务内容是请2号详细介绍ICP许可证的知识（定义、适用人群、办理流程、与其他牌照的区别）\n3. 把2号的回复整理后汇报给0号"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":52831,"output":2973,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55804,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776758732834,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8ce5be9c-8b5b-90e9-863a-89bf668de306"}}
