{"type":"message","id":"c16ce767","parentId":"337adfaa","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:06:07.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so I've spawned 1号. Let me wait for its completion event. It should:\n1. Acknowledge the task from 0号\n2. Spawn 2号 with a sessions_spawn call\n3. Report back\n\nLet me wait for the result.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"第一棒已发出：**0号 → 1号·品牌虾**。\n\n1号需要：\n1. 确认收到转派\n2. **亲自调用工具生成2号子代理**去问ICP许可证的事\n3. 整理2号结果汇报给我\n\n等1号的反馈，接着我会让1号再生成3号……一路接力到8号 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":54706,"output":198,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54904,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776758765111,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f706f1c7-2e7b-9864-b0e7-4362ffa8aab7"}}
