{"type":"message","id":"45cf9841","parentId":"ea549d58","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:07:08.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to maintain the flow. 3号 is done, 4B is now spawned. I will wait for its result before spawning 5B. Keep it concise in my reply.\nDone. \n[Proceeds]\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞 **3号完成，接力棒已交到4B手中。** \n\n4B将从**成交转化和定价策略**角度回答ICP许可证问题。同时会明确签约后移交给谁（5A/5B代办虾）以及交接清单。等结果回来我立刻推给下一棒 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":58384,"output":166,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58550,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776758826790,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7135077b-6783-9363-b533-e77bf776a388"}}
