{"type":"message","id":"ee58c0f3","parentId":"9089f387","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:07:32.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"接力棒传了：**0→1→2→3→4B→5A→6号售后** 已在执行。\n\n等6号的结果，然后继续推给7号数据虾 🦞","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞 **5A完成，6号售后接力已发出。**\n\n6号将从**获证后维护、续期提醒、延伸销售、投诉预防**四个维度回答ICP客户的后续服务链。同时会梳理清楚可以打包卖给谁做二次销售 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":61073,"output":152,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61225,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776758850408,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7febf69a-84dd-9ca3-804f-f4bb0d360a09"}}
