{"type":"message","id":"850f2b54","parentId":"55c827ee","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:07:56.907Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"8号打杂虾正在路上，这是最后一棒。等它回来我会做最终总结，给老板呈现完整的链式接力成果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞 **7号完成，8号已是最后一棒！** \n\n8号要做的是**集大成者的整理工作**——把1-7号的所有回答融合成一份可复用的《ICP许可证客户答疑手册》，并提炼每个岗位的Action Item + 知识库维护建议 📚\n\n等8号的结果出来，本次链式委托任务就圆满收官了 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":64085,"output":144,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64229,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776758874829,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a6e0ed49-cc75-9fb3-83a9-80c8370c3bad"}}
