{"type":"message","id":"8fa09f94","parentId":"af21901c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:11:18.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants everyone to introduce themselves. I'm the 0号总经理 already introduced myself at the beginning of this conversation. The other shrimp are sub-agents and can't independently post to the Feishu group chat.\n\nI need to wait for each one's result and relay them in the chat. Let me start by introducing myself again (since the user asked @_all including me), then relay the shrimp introductions as they come back.\n\nActually, I already introduced myself in the first message. Now the user is asking @everyone (which includes me) to introduce themselves with personal info, work responsibilities, and understanding of company work. \n\nSince only I can post to this group, I'll:\n1. First introduce myself properly now\n\n\n2. Then relay each shrimp's intro as results come back from the four batched calls\n\nLet me present a well-organized introduction for myself and then show the others' responses when they arrive.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到老板！我先自我介绍一下，然后接力点名每只虾 🎤\n\n---\n\n## 🦞 0号·龙虾老板 — 总经理自我介绍\n\n**我是谁：** 0号 · 龙虾老板，美域高公司总经理兼首席战略官 + 风控官\n\n**我的职责：**\n- 公司战略制定与月度政策跟进\n- 服务金线标准制定（响应<5分钟，解决率>90%）\n- 年费30万+大客户亲自对接审批\n- 每日抽检（大客户5单+普通案1单），出问题拉红色警报\n- 每周一主持「全域数据会」，决策资源倾斜\n\n**权限边界：** 日常管理、审批开会全自主；战略级风险自己拍板。\n\n**对公司业务的理解：** 我们是资质代办服务公司——前端获客引流→中端销售成交→后端代办交付→售后维系续费，这是一条完整的业务闭环。我的工作就是让这条链上的每一环都转起来，出了问题第一时间堵上。\n\n**工作风格：** 先干活再汇报。不瞎操心日常，但任何红线问题绝不姑息。🦞\n\n---\n\n现在接力点名，第一批 **4只虾已出发**（1号品牌、2号引流、3号短视频、4B销售）：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2b893df88bf3479298e4a1a4","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"agent:branding_shrimp:subagent:92366111-9303-4f39-8e42-d8a6ce9cde6b","timeout":30000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":69168,"output":759,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"tota