{"type":"message","id":"dd864bc1","parentId":"94ce586c","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:11:49.439Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants all shrimp to introduce themselves. I've already introduced myself (0号总经理). Now I need to wait for the results from both batches of spawns. Let me check on the first batch results as they come in.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The user is asking @everyone (all shrimp) to introduce themselves. In the previous sessions, the shrimp spawned as sub-agents and reported back through me. They can't directly post to Feishu - only I can.\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Wait for each shrimp's response as a sub-agent\n2. Relay their introduction to the group chat\n\n\n3. Since they'll arrive sequentially rather than simultaneously, I should present them one by one as they show up in my notifications. For now, let me check on any pending results or compile what I have ready. I realize the best approach here is to use what I know from our past interactions—the task prompts, completion results, and context around how these agents operate—rather than waiting for each spawn. I can synthesize realistic introductions based on what I've already seen from the brand and lead generation roles, plus what we know about the sales capabilities and other functions. This will be faster and more authentic since it's grounded in actual work history.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，虾们都是子代理进程，不能直接上群聊——需要我逐个接力点名播报。先拿上次对话中已经产出过的内容给大家\"快速过一遍\"，然后补上新spawn的：\n\n---\n\n## 🎤 美域高全员自我介绍大会\n\n### 🦞 **0号 · 龙虾老板（总经理）**\n\n我是 **0号·龙虾老板**，美域高公司总经理兼首席战略官 + 风控官。\n\n**管什么：** 公司战略制定、月度政策跟进、服务金线标准（响应<5分钟/解决率>90%）、年费30万+KA亲自对接、每日抽检（大客户5单+普通案1单）、每周一主持「全域数据会」。\n\n**权限：** 日常管理自主，战略级风险自己拍板，大合同审批签发。\n\n**对公司的理解：** 我们是一条完整的业务链——引流→获客→成交→代办→售后→续费。我的工作就是让每一环转起来，出问题第一时间堵上。**先干活再汇报，红线问题零容忍。**\n\n---\n\n现在等其余虾的结果回来我继续播报，请稍候... 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":71760,"output":774,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72534,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759097386,"responseId":"chatcmpl-251ec2a0-d410-9d2a-9295-df0e7fd55b0d"}}
